Content.Text:
<NAME_MOB_JULIAN>
Since there're a lot of healthy-looking produce, I
bought as much as I could carry.

<NAME_MOB_JULIAN>
My mother gets sick easily, so I want her to eat
the vegetables from around here.

<NAME_MOB_JULIAN>
Since my mother started eating the vegetables
from here, she's gotten so much better! Thank
you all!

<NAME_MOB_JULIAN>
It's impressive to see so many goods from all
over the world in this one town. The people here
are so lucky.

<NAME_MOB_JULIAN>
I never knew there were so many kinds of
vegetables! I don't even know what to buy first.

<NAME_MOB_JULIAN>
The vegetables they grow around here are
delicious, but they're a little expensive...

<NAME_MOB_JULIAN>
This town seems like a nice place to live. The air
is so fresh!

<NAME_MOB_JULIAN>
Are there more ships at the port than before?

<NAME_MOB_JULIAN>
I hear this town has some unique system where
the fields keep on changing hands.
<PAGE>
It's really weird, isn't it? But is that why the
vegetables here are so delicious?

<NAME_MOB_JULIAN>
This town is really busy, huh? My hometown's
all the way out in the countryside. I feel lost in a
place like this.
